CUCUMBER
rake cucumber        # Alias for cucumber:ok
rake cucumber:all    # Run all features
rake cucumber:ok     # Run features that should pass
rake cucumber:rerun  # Record failing features and run only them if any exist
rake cucumber:wip    # Run features that are being worked on



To run scenarios with a specific tag:
cucumber --tags @tagname

To exclude scenarios with a certain tag, prefix the tag with a tilde:
cucumber --tags ~@wip

To run a specific feature file
cucumber -r features features/xxxxxxxxx.feature

To run with the progress bar
 cucumber -f progress

DB test
rake db:migrate RAILS_ENV=test
rake db:test:clone
rails g cucumber:install

GIT USEFUL COMMANDS
git reset --hard